and physician colleagues).</p>
 
<p>OIG hopes you find these free educational materials helpful and appreciates your willingness to
educate physicians about fraud, waste, and abuse.</p>

<a target="_blank" href="http://www.cms.gov/Outreach-and-Education/Medicare-Learning-Network-MLN/MLNGenInfo/index.html"><img class="r" src="/compliance/101/images/cme.jpg" width="100" alt="Visit the Medicare Learning Network" /></a>
<p>Physicians can earn Category 1 continuing medical education (CME) credit by completing the Avoiding Medicare Fraud and Abuse: A Roadmap for Physicians course from the Medicare Learning Network. <a href="/compliance/101/cme.asp">Learn more</a>.</p>
 

